{"tid":1129353,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂 Switch 特價週，多款遊戲優惠低至5 折！","createTime":"2019-04-28T12:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T11:16:31.000Z","uid":43009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c05d9e9567e02f8763c8df9ed4f255ce090806b1","tid":1129353,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T12:08:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://pc3mag.com/switch-games-jetso201904/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fswitch-games-jetso201904%2F&d=chjGuQxbuHnWuKCrZ0Kyvvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=6725e73c\" target=\"_blank\">http://pc3mag.com/switch-games-jetso201904/</a><br />\n<br />\n為慶祝即將到來的日本黃金周，任天堂Switch日本地區官方將開啟「黃金週特賣」線上活動，由4月25日起至5月8日，多款遊戲開啟減價優惠活動。遊戲包括《超級馬里歐：奧德賽》、《馬里歐賽車8豪華版》、《星之卡比新星同盟》《馬里歐網球ACE》等任天堂遊戲有7折優惠，而《Othello》更做到半價的折扣，是入手 ONLINE SHOP 遊戲的好時刻！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pc3mag.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/PhotoGrid_1555990179244_compress_35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FPhotoGrid_1555990179244_compress_35.jpg&h=001b4727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n活動確實優惠定於日本時間2019年4月25日（星期四）至5月8日（星期三）23：59舉行。到時只要登入日本地區的任天堂 ONLINE SHOP 帳號，便可購買，安裝下載至 Switch 遊戲機便可直接玩。未有日本帳號的讀者，可申請多個選擇日本地區即可，或在本身帳號更改為日本地區，有興趣購買可參考以下名單："},{"pid":"acfd6649f912adee663039c83892a508c7a12539","tid":1129353,"uid":43009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pc3mag.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Screenshot-2019-04-23-at-11.06.00-AM_compress_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FScreenshot-2019-04-23-at-11.06.00-AM_compress_4.jpg&h=f6cfa770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://pc3mag.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Screenshot-2019-04-23-at-11.08.06-AM_compress_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpc3mag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2FScr